Value: Autosports Group Limited, together with its subsidiaries, engages in the motor vehicle retailing business in Australia. It sells new and used motor vehicles, aftermarket products, and spare parts; distributes finance and insurance products; and provides motor vehicle servicing and collision repair services. As of June 30, 2021, it operates 43 franchised dealerships; 3 used motor vehicle outlets; and 6 motor vehicle collision repair facilities. Autosports Group Limited was founded in 2006 and is based in Leichhardt, Australia.
